<h2>UChan Imageboard - A Brief Overview</h2>
(University Channel)
<br><br>

“An imageboard is a type of Internet forum that revolves around the anonymous posting of images, often alongside related text and discussion. It is aimed to create insightful discussion as the anonymous nature of imageboards promote the emphasis on what is said rather than who is saying it.”
<br><br>

The idea: An online university ‘Freedom Wall’.
<br><br>

The motivation: A University centered imageboard would be a fun experiment / way to have students connect with one another anonymously especially during this pandemic where communication with one another is limited online. 
<br><br>

Read more on Imageboard
